Daughter been pestering Lulu to read
book of creation of Alst to her.

rows.label: tlk42300071_01_msg0002
rows.name:
You think Lulu should read to her?
But have already read book to
daughter 700 times!

rows.label: tlk42300071_01_msg0003
rows.name:
She keep asking questions while
reading too, and Lulu have no idea
how to answer.

rows.label: tlk42300071_01_msg0004
rows.name:
"What is favorite food of Divine Beast? Does
Divine Beast sink if it sleeps? Is it girl or boy?"
Me not know these things!
